{"tid":1538772,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲迪克當上18-19歐聯跑速最快球員","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:41:05.000Z","uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf046484a868d0e11d821cb432fd6d3ab0cced1","tid":1538772,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:08.000Z","msg":"雲迪克在上屆4強首回合作客巴塞隆拿一仗，於一次回防追截時速度高達34.5km/h，成功阻截了美斯傳球予隊友佐迪艾巴的路線。<br />\n<br />\n該速度力壓辛尼的34.4km/h、獲加的34.2km/h以及巴利的33.8km/h成為上屆最快的衝刺，令雲迪克當上歐聯最快球員。<br />\n<br />\n阿積士前鋒杜辛泰迪治則以平均每仗多達62.25次衝刺，在上屆賽事成為每仗衝刺次數最多的球員，力壓第2位的荷西卡利祖。<br />\n<br />\n至於國際米蘭中場波索域以每仗平均每分鐘跑動達137.3米，擊敗艾歷臣及占士米拿成為此排行榜首位。"},{"pid":"b000e1f97032b5b1e7d8ba0ebc5f0f5713ec75fa","tid":1538772,"uid":17057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"呢個高度有呢個速度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500125d260495c89b74ae5712ca7a056c8cb8faf","tid":1538772,"uid":165817,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"佢上季直頭fit到唔係人類咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f57df676524db7b822510e5d17f8ea35f1ecd0e","tid":1538772,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"後退帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheRedmenTV/status/1168867868114640896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheRedmenTV%2Fstatus%2F1168867868114640896&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEqyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=583c2611\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheRedmenTV%2Fstatus%2F1168867868114640896&h=7694b8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheRedmenTV/status/1168867868114640896</a>"},{"pid":"353f715cb9bd9af1151c3d6b1038abc4c9229ce3","tid":1538772,"uid":48222,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20